      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the S54-powered icon, maintained to an exacting standard. The 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six features a meticulously serviced double-VANOS system and rod bearings, ensuring the 8,000 RPM redline is reached with mechanical harmony. Power is routed through a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock. The chassis has been proactively reinforced at the rear subframe mounting points to eliminate common structural fatigue. The factory finish remains deep and lustrous, free of rock chips or oxidation, while the cabin retains its original tactile integrity with no bolster wear or interior trim delamination. This is a turn-key, investment-grade specimen for the discerning collector who demands mechanical perfection.",
