      "description": "Presented in truly pristine, showroom-level condition, this vehicle is a rare find for the discerning collector or enthusiast. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, reflecting its life spent exclusively in a climate-controlled garage. Inside, the cabin remains in an untouched state; the premium leather upholstery is firm and free of any wear or aging, while the high-tech interface and every tactile control operate with the precision of a brand-new car. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, having followed a rigorous maintenance schedule with every service documented. The engine note is smooth and purposeful, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. This is a one-owner vehicle that has never seen inclement weather, offering a driving experience that is indistinguishable from the day it first left the dealership. Every detail, from the flawless alloy wheels to the original factory scent, confirms its status as a top-tier specimen.",
